<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>Night Dice — Privacy Policy</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #223843;
    --bg2: #1b2d36;
    --card: rgba(239,241,243,0.06);
    --line: rgba(219,211,216,0.18);
    --ink: #EFF1F3;
    --muted: #DBD3D8;
    --accent: #D77A61;
    --sand: #D8B4A0;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }
  .wrap { max-width: 740px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 48px 22px 80px; }
  header { margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .brand { font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); }
  .brand b { color: var(--accent); }
  h1 { font-size: 30px; font-weight: 800; margin: 14px 0 6px; }
  .updated { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; }
  h2 { font-size: 19px; margin: 34px 0 8px; color: var(--sand); }
  p, li { color: var(--ink); }
  .muted { color: var(--muted); }
  a { color: var(--accent); }
  ul { padding-left: 20px; }
  li { margin: 6px 0; }
  .card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    margin: 18px 0;
  }
  .pill {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(215,122,97,0.18);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 13px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  footer { margin-top: 48px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); padding-top: 18px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; }
  footer a { color: var(--sand); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <header>
      <div class="brand">NIGHT <b>DICE</b></div>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="updated">Last updated: June 9, 2026</div>
    </header>

    <div class="card">
      <span class="pill">The short version</span>
      <p><strong>Night Dice does not collect, store, or share any of your personal
      information.</strong> The app has no accounts, no analytics, no advertising,
      and no tracking. It does not connect to the internet to send your data
      anywhere. Everything you enter stays on your device.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>Information we collect</h2>
    <p><strong>None.</strong> Night Dice does not collect any personal data about you.
    We do not ask you to create an account, and we do not have access to any
    information you enter in the app.</p>

    <h2>Information stored on your device</h2>
    <p>To keep score, the app saves the following <em>locally on your device only</em>:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Player names you type in when setting up a game.</li>
      <li>Scores and scorecards for your games.</li>
      <li>Completed games (your History) and one in-progress game you can resume.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>This information never leaves your device. It is not transmitted to us or to
    any third party. If you delete the app, this data is permanently removed.</p>

    <h2>Analytics, advertising &amp; tracking</h2>
    <p>Night Dice contains <strong>no analytics, no advertising, no third-party SDKs,
    and no tracking technologies</strong>. We do not use cookies or identifiers, and
    we do not track you across apps or websites.</p>

    <h2>Network access</h2>
    <p>The app functions fully offline. It does not require an internet connection and
    does not transmit your data over a network.</p>

    <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
    <p>Night Dice does not knowingly collect personal information from anyone, including
    children. Because some games reference adult themes (for example, choosing who
    "buys the round"), the app is rated for older audiences in the App Store. No data
    is collected from any user regardless of age.</p>

    <h2>Your control</h2>
    <p>Because all data lives only on your device, you are always in control. You can
    clear your History entries within the app, discard an in-progress game, or remove
    everything by deleting the app from your device.</p>

    <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p>If this policy changes, we will update this page and revise the "Last updated"
    date above.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy? Email
    <a href="mailto:bideapp@gmail.com">bideapp@gmail.com</a>.</p>

    <footer>
      Night Dice is an unofficial scorekeeping and rules-reference app. Game names are
      used descriptively to identify traditional games; any trademarks belong to their
      respective owners. &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="support.html">Help &amp; Support</a>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
